  "Subject": "Important: Event Cancelled \u0026 Account Notice \u2014 Manoj Prabakar Standap Comedy | Chennai",
  "Body": "\u003C!DOCTYPE html\u003E\n\u003Chtml\u003E\n\u003Chead\u003E\n  \u003Cmeta charset=\u0022utf-8\u0022 /\u003E\n  \u003Cstyle\u003E\n    body {\n      font-family: \u0027Segoe UI\u0027, Arial, sans-serif;\n      background-color: #ffffff;\n      color: #000000;\n      margin: 0;\n      padding: 0;\n    }\n    .container {\n      max-width: 520px;\n      margin: 40px auto;\n      background-color: #ffffff;\n      border: 3px solid #000000;\n      border-radius: 0px;\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    .header {\n      background-color: #1a1a2e;\n      padding: 32px;\n      text-align: center;\n      border-bottom: 3px solid #000000;\n    }\n    .header h1 {\n      color: #ffffff;\n      margin: 0 0 6px;\n      font-size: 22px;\n      font-weight: 800;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 2px;\n    }\n    .header p {\n      color: #a0aec0;\n      margin: 0;\n      font-size: 13px;\n    }\n    .body {\n      padding: 40px;\n    }\n    .body p {\n      color: #1a1a2e;\n      font-size: 15px;\n      line-height: 1.7;\n      margin: 0 0 18px;\n    }\n    .info-box {\n      background-color: #0f0f1a;\n      border-left: 4px solid #e53e3e;\n      padding: 22px 24px;\n      margin: 28px 0;\n      color: #ffffff;\n    }\n    .info-title {\n      font-size: 11px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 1.5px;\n      color: #fc8181;\n      margin-bottom: 14px;\n    }\n    .info-item {\n      font-size: 14px;\n      margin-bottom: 10px;\n      line-height: 1.5;\n      color: #e2e8f0;\n    }\n    .info-label {\n      font-weight: 700;\n      color: #fc8181;\n    }\n    .account-status-box {\n      background-color: #fff5f5;\n      border: 2px solid #fc8181;\n      padding: 20px 24px;\n      margin: 20px 0;\n    }\n    .account-status-box p {\n      color: #742a2a;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      margin: 0;\n      line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n    .refund-note {\n      font-size: 13px;\n      color: #4a5568;\n      border-left: 3px solid #48bb78;\n      padding-left: 14px;\n      margin-top: 24px;\n      line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n    .footer {\n      background-color: #0f0f1a;\n      color: #718096;\n      padding: 20px;\n      text-align: center;\n      font-size: 11px;\n      border-top: 3px solid #000000;\n      letter-spacing: 1px;\n    }\n  \u003C/style\u003E\n\u003C/head\u003E\n\u003Cbody\u003E\n  \u003Cdiv class=\u0022container\u0022\u003E\n    \u003Cdiv class=\u0022header\u0022\u003E\n      \u003Ch1\u003E\u003Cstrong style=\u0022color: #ffffff; font-weight: 800;\u0022\u003EGetMyEvents\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h1\u003E\n      \u003Cp\u003EPlatform Policy \u0026amp; Account Notice\u003C/p\u003E\n    \u003C/div\u003E\n    \u003Cdiv class=\u0022body\u0022\u003E\n      \u003Cp\u003EDear Charu Keerthi,\u003C/p\u003E\n      \u003Cp\u003E\n        Following a thorough review of a report filed against one of your events, our Trust \u0026amp; Safety team has upheld the report.\n        As a result, the following actions have been taken on your account and event.\n      \u003C/p\u003E\n\n      \u003Cdiv class=\u0022info-box\u0022\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022info-title\u0022\u003E\u0026#9888; Action Summary\u003C/div\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022info-item\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022info-label\u0022\u003EEvent:\u003C/span\u003E Manoj Prabakar Standap Comedy | Chennai\u003C/div\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022info-item\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022info-label\u0022\u003EEvent Status:\u003C/span\u003E Cancelled\u003C/div\u003E\n      \u003C/div\u003E\n\n      \u003Cdiv class=\u0022account-status-box\u0022\u003E\n        \u003Cp\u003EYour account has been \u003Cstrong\u003ERestricted\u003C/strong\u003E. You may no longer create new events or access organizer features until this restriction is reviewed and lifted.\u003C/p\u003E\n      \u003C/div\u003E\n\n      \u003Cp class=\u0022refund-note\u0022\u003E\n        All attendees who had confirmed bookings for \u003Cstrong\u003EManoj Prabakar Standap Comedy | Chennai\u003C/strong\u003E have been notified and will receive a \u003Cstrong\u003Efull refund\u003C/strong\u003E to their original payment method within 5\u0026ndash;10 business days, depending on their bank or card provider.\n      \u003C/p\u003E\n\n      \u003Cp style=\u0022margin-top: 28px;\u0022\u003E\n        If you wish to appeal this decision or have any questions regarding this notice, please contact our support team directly. We are committed to maintaining a fair and transparent platform for all users.\n      \u003C/p\u003E\n\n      \u003Cp\u003E\n        Thank you for your understanding.\u003Cbr /\u003E\n        \u003Cstrong\u003EGetMyEvents Trust \u0026amp; Safety Team\u003C/strong\u003E\n      \u003C/p\u003E\n    \u003C/div\u003E\n    \u003Cdiv class=\u0022footer\u0022\u003E\n      \u0026copy; 2026 GetMyEvents. All rights reserved.\n    \u003C/div\u003E\n  \u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/body\u003E\n\u003C/html\u003E\n"
}